    <item>
      <title>马克龙选择不在约 60 个选区派候选人参加选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/macron-allies-not-fielding-candidates-in-60-electoral-districts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理加布里埃尔·阿塔尔表示，法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的政党及其盟友将不会在约 60 个选区派出候选人，以便为其他更有机会阻止极右翼和新左翼联盟的政党扫清道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/macron-allies-not-fielding-candidates-in-60-electoral-districts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 06:50:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国与菲律宾就最新船只碰撞事件细节发生争执</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/china-reports-ship-collision-which-manila-calls-misleading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国海岸警卫队称，中国和菲律宾船只在南海斯普拉特利群岛附近海域发生碰撞，但马尼拉称北京的说法“具有误导性”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/china-reports-ship-collision-which-manila-calls-misleading</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 06:40:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度火车相撞至少造成 8 人死亡，数十人受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-17/urgent-trains-collide-in-eastern-india-killing-at-least-5-with-rescue-work-ongoing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新德里（美联社）——官员称，周一，一列货运列车与一列客运列车在印度东部西孟加拉邦相撞，造成至少 8 人死亡，数人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-17/urgent-trains-collide-in-eastern-india-killing-at-least-5-with-rescue-work-ongoing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 05:32:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
